<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />Say to God, "How terrifying are your deeds!</para>

<para style="q1">By the greatness of your power your enemies will submit to you.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />All the earth will worship you</para>

<para style="q1">and will sing to you;</para>

<para style="q1">they will sing to your name."

<char style="qs">Selah</char></para>
